        h3.text-muted OurService
      .jumbotron
        h1 Turn strangers into friends!
        p.lead It could be easy with OurSevice, help make it happen
        ul
          li Beta Program - $19.95 Be involved with the testing, see it first!
            a(href='#beta') ~Learn more
          li Lifetime - $299 Exclusive perks for early backers
            a(href='#lifetime') ~Learn more
          li Regular Membership - $9.95/month or $99/year on release
        i.text-center  Beta and Lifetime are limited time offerings to help launch ourService
        div
          i.text-center  While in beta OurService is paid sign-up only
      .row.marketing
        h1 About OurService
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Say what!?
          p
            | Our service looks to empower people to connect with strangers in a fast,
            | safe and convienient way, through timed text.
            | Sure, strangers are inherently strange, yet most of our best friends or
            | invaluble professional peers start off an strangers to us. Some of them
            | even remain strange long after becoming aquented! OurService acts a gateway
            | to creating a strong connection, providing a new shared context with
            | people of simiar interest.
          h4 Give me friends?
          p
            | It should be noted that OurService holds no promise of forcing anyone to be
            | your friend. OurService hopes to help create situations where any two users become
            | comfortable with each other enough that they want to continue the conversation
            | regularly IRL ( in real life ) or in more identifing contexts like other networks,
            | phone, or video chat.
        .col-lg-6
          h4 How does it work?
          p
            | It realy easy to get started! Just type any topic that interest you at the
            | moment and ourService shows your topic to similar users or just whoever happens
            | to be on at the time. If the topic peaks someone interest they can select it
            | and WHAMIE BAM! They are in a real time conversation with you. Simple as that. Stop
            | talking to repeat the process, keep talking to potentially make a new friend.
          h4 Is OurService Anonomous?
          p
            | Short answer is yes, the long answer is NO.
            | Asking, anonmous to who? Makes this question more clear.
            | By default, no one needs to use an identy in order to use OurService besides paying to sign-up.
            | Effectively, given two users have never talked before they are in simple terms
            | anonomous to one another.
            | Once users get talking, our paying customers can label users they have had good conversations
            | with. The label basically favorites the person so that if they are on again our robots know to
            | prioritize making the match again.
          p
            | OurService, does keep track of everyone by a unique ID and stores unique words
            | that they use in order to determine which other users might want to see their topics. OurService
            | strictly uses user data to provide value to the service and its parent companies. Please
            | see our privacy policy for more details about how the data can and cannot be used.
      // beta program
      #beta.jumbotron
        .row
          h1 Beta: Help us get started!
          h2.lead Be part of the begining of something that will be great
          .col-lg-6
            p Will include the following
              li Become part of founding ecosytem
              li Make friends with folks in your profession that will be targeted for beta
            i.text-center  Service acccess till the time of full release ( 2-4 months )
          .col-lg-6
            a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success(href='#signup') Sign up $19.95
      .row
        h1  About Beta
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Becoming part of the ecosystem
          p
            | It may be a bit quite at first, but OurService will grow to be bustling place.
            | Watching this ecosystem grow will be a unique experience.
            | Right now we imagine OurServices will be helpfull for
            | proffesional and social developent of Office and IT prossionals that type regularly enough to
            | be good text conversationalist already. Who knows though, maybe people who rarely type
            | will find a new found reason to! OurService can empower them in more than one way.
          h4 Unique situation
          p
            | Beta and Lifetime users will share the unique context of being on the service first.
            | The first Beta users will be likely mostly be based in Southern NH because that
            | is where OurService is being developed.
            | Many people might already know each other or have a friend of a friend
            | in common on OurService but they will only ever find out by chatting.
        .col-lg-6
          h4 Shape what happens
          p
            | There are basic design rules to how OurSerice works, but ultimately our beta users are
            | really going to show where OurService can be valuable.
          h4 Beta goals
          p
            | OurService is going to be a great resource for finding unique serendipidous interactions
            | Gaining the critical mass is important for this, but first we are going to have help
            | making sure the wrinkles are ironed out and we can handle influx of a lot of use. Beta
            | is an opportunity to get in on the ground floor and see the possibilities and have
            | the first interactions that lead to those possibilities.
      // sign up form
      #signup.jumbotron
        h1 Sign up for OurService!
        form(method='post')
          input(type='hidden', name="_csrf", value=csrfToken)
          .form-group
            label(for='signupEmail')  Email Address
            input#signupEmail.form-control(type='email', name="email")
          .form-group
            label(for='signupPassword')  Password
            input#signupPassword.form-control(type='password', name="password")
          .form-group
            label(for='confirmPassword')  Confirm Password
            input#confirmPassword.form-control(type='password', name="confirmPassword")
          .radio
            label
              input#planOption1(type='radio', name='optionsRadios', value='Beta', checked='')
              |                             Beta $19.95
          .radio
            label
              input#planOption2(type='radio', name='optionsRadios', value='Lifetime')
              |                             Lifetime $299
          .form-group
            label(for='signupBilling')  Billing info
            input#confirmPassword.form-control(type='password')
          input#submit.btn.btn-lg.btn-success(type='submit', value='submit')
