          h1 Lifetime: Say you made it possible
          h2.lead Limited time exclusive option to early adopters
          .col-lg-6
            p
              | Will include the following
              li Life time service access
              li Special attention, to increase quality of service
              li Recongnition of support
            i.text-center  We will have a backer&apos;s wall in the about section of our site
          .col-lg-6
            a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success(href='#signup') Sign up $299
