            | Watching this ecosystem grow will be a unique experience.
            | Right now we imagine OurServices will be helpfull for
            | proffesional and social developent of Office and IT prossionals that type regularly enough to
            | be good text conversationalist already. Who knows though, maybe people who rarely type
            | will find a new found reason to! OurService can empower them in more than one way.
          h4 Your name on the wall
          p
            | Lifetime members forever have a place in our offical about page. People often say &quot;When you
            | make it, remember everyone that helped&quot;. We plan to.
          h4 Personal support
          p
            | The OurService team will always work closley with our lifetime members to make sure OurService
            | provides the best value it can. Lifetime members have backed us and we aim to return the favor
            | ten fold.
        .col-lg-6
          blockquote
            p
              | Getting a business going is a rosey thing from the outside. It is easy to see all of
              | the successes and the present glory those successes have.
            p
              | &quot;Truth is, starting something from nothing is a long strugle.
              | Creating a company that provides more value than it takes is something I have
              | worked at for a number of years. The only reason any of this can be possible is
              | the continuing suport of family, friends, future friends and living in a place
              | that celebrates the pursuit of dreams. Lifetime membership provides more than the value of
              | OurService for life, it reconizes that you are core believer
              | in the OurService team and myself&quot;
            footer
              | Paul Beaudet
              cite(title='Source Title') CEO OurService
